# Databricks supply-chain-safe npm proxy. Per go/npm-registry-access,
# this is the canonical dev-laptop registry. Note: the proxy filters
# package versions released within the last 7 days — if a package fails
# to install with what looks like a 502, that's almost certainly the
# age filter; ask in #npm-registry-access.
registry=https://npm-proxy.cloud.databricks.com/
